<paragraph base="F45931101" id="IFRS16_C19"><paranum>C19</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="C19"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0673">If a <xref base="F45929736" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0380">lessee<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0220"/></ph></xref> previously recognised an asset or a liability applying <xref base="F47961475" href="../ifrs03/IFRS03_TOC.dita#IFRS03_TOC0001/IFRS03_TOC0001_V2" id="IFRS16_X0524"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 3</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Business Combinations</ph></ph></xref> relating to favourable or unfavourable terms of an <xref base="F45929764" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0384">operating lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0269"/></ph></xref> acquired as part of a business combination, the lessee shall derecognise that asset or liability and adjust the carrying amount of the <xref base="F45929827" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0388">right-of-use asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0342"/></ph></xref> by a corresponding amount at the date of initial application.</p></body></paragraph>